    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but they shouldn't have to. it’s not right that they spend their weekends or their evenings just managing my life. i spent my whole life taking care of them and my husband, and now it's like the roles have flipped and everyone is just... drained. i look at them and i just feel so guilty. sometimes i think if i wasn't here, they could finally just breathe and live their own lives without having to worry about me all the time.",
