    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's not that kind of relief i'm looking for. i don't think a support group is going to change the fact that i'm just... slowing them down. it feels so selfish to keep holding on when i know it's making their lives harder. do you think it's selfish to want to just... go quietly? to not make it a big thing, but just make it so they don't have to worry anymore?",
